[src:pytest-fixtures-lib/test-double] For service-oriented architecture (SOA) systems and microservices, testers use test doubles that communicate with the system under test over a network protocol.
[src:pytest-fixtures-lib/test-double] These test doubles are called by different names by the tool vendors.
[src:pytest-fixtures-lib/test-double] A commonly used term is service virtualization.
